long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Traceless is a Chrome extension that provides users with the ability to search the web in incognito mode. This feature ensures that your browsing history and search queries are not recorded. When the extension is opened, users have the option to search in incognito, providing them with an additional layer of privacy and security.

In addition to its incognito search feature, Traceless offers three different settings for clearing data. The first setting allows users to clear their browsing history and cache, while the second setting goes a step further by also deleting history, cache, download history, files from local storage, and cookies. The third and final setting deletes all of this plus app cache.

These settings provide users with different levels of data deletion, allowing them to choose the one that best fits their needs. This extension is perfect for users who value privacy and want to have control over the data that is stored on their device.

Traceless is easy to use, and its interface is intuitive. With just a few clicks, you can search in incognito and clear your browsing data, giving you peace of mind knowing that your online activities are private and your data is secure.

Overall, Traceless is a must-have extension for users who want to search the web without leaving a trace. It provides a convenient and secure way to browse the internet while keeping your online.
